---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
const title = "Great Northern Digital Labs";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>{title}</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Great Northern Digital Labs – making technology quietly useful in everyday life."
    />
  </head>

  <body
    style="
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: #050816;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    "
  >
    <main style="max-width: 720px; width: 100%;">
      <!-- BIG OBVIOUS LOGO BLOCK -->
      <div
        style="
          display: flex;
          justify-content: flex-start;
          margin-bottom: 2rem;
        "
      >
      <img src="/GNDLIslandLogoWhite.png" alt="Great Northern Digital Labs" />

      </div>

      <h1 style="font-size: 1.4rem; margin: 0 0 0.4rem 0;">
        Great Northern Digital Labs
      </h1>

      <p style="margin: 0 0 1.4rem 0; font-size: 0.95rem; opacity: 0.75;">
        Making technology quietly useful in everyday life.
      </p>

      <p style="line-height: 1.7;">
        Great Northern Digital Labs is a small northern skunkworks focused on
        making technology work in real people’s everyday lives. We tinker,
        prototype, and experiment until strange ideas become practical tools
        you can actually use.
      </p>

      <p style="line-height: 1.7;">
        Around here, we’re not afraid of odd projects or rough edges. We
        specialize in <strong>attempting the idiotic, using the impractical,
        to do the impossible</strong> — and then quietly packaging the results
        into reliable systems and services.
      </p>

      <p style="line-height: 1.7; margin-top: 1.6rem;">
        This is a temporary home while new experiments spin up. For inquiries,
        collaborations, or delightfully weird ideas, email
        <a
          href="mailto:info@gndl.ca"
          style="color: #28e0ff; text-decoration: none;"
        >
          info@gndl.ca
        </a>.
      </p>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
